lead_paragraph: SHERIDAN--Josephine nee Biggins, 78, died peacefully July 4, 2016 in her home in Barnegat, NJ. Survived by husband, Peter F. Sheridan, children; Peter T., Thomas F. (Vincent Walsh), Catherine (John), Ann (Erich Steinbrunn) and Maureen, sister, Mary Ellen Desmond "Nana" to Jack, Cara, Colleen and Tyler, 16 nieces and nephews. Visiting is Sunday from 4-8pm at Assumma-Shankey Funeral Home. Funeral, Monday, 10:30am, The Chapel at St. Dominics, Blauvelt, NY. Private burial. 1/3

headline.main: Paid Notice: Deaths  SHERIDAN, JOSEPHINE NEE BIGGINS
